Instruction Art Submission, eugeneOBJ

How to Ollie on a Skateboard

Step 1: Stand on Skateboard
Step 2: Place back foot on the Tail of the skateboard
Step 3: Place front foot directly behind the screws
Step 4: Snap back foot down till the Tail of the skateboard hits the ground
Step 5: Drag front foot forward, parallel to the lenght of the skateboard
Step 6: Jump upward concurrently while performing steps 4 & 5

End.
